HEADWORD: Acosmist
<hw>A*cos"mist</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Acosmism</er>.]</ety> <def>One who denies the existence of the
universe, or of a universe as distinct from God.</def> <rj><au>G. H.
Lewes.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

